                            <comment id="13896454" author="mreutegg" created="Mon, 10 Feb 2014 12:52:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The two graphs show the current behavior on a oak-run benchmark running CreateManyNodesTest. A lot of time spent in persist() is waiting for the background thread to finish the cache invalidation.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13897762" author="mreutegg" created="Tue, 11 Feb 2014 11:44:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Initial work done in &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1567066&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1567066&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13917929" author="mreutegg" created="Mon, 3 Mar 2014 10:45:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Further decoupled background write from local commits.&lt;/p&gt;

